---
title: Mediterranean Mozzarella Paninis Serves 2 | with Basil Pesto and Roasted Peppers
description: This veggie panini is anything but boring, loaded with melted fresh mozzarella and briny roasted red peppers. An herby pesto mayo brings the whole sandwich together for a delicious toasted bite!
